Investors





Achieving optimal returns on solar investments
Solar energy systems that are well planned, built and managed are compelling and reliable investment opportunities for debt and equity providers. Nexamp’s solar facilities are designed to optimize ROI for tax equity and sponsor equity providers. They consistently meet the highest standards of quality to ensure long-term asset integrity and performance.
We work with solar energy investor clients to identify investment parameters and deliver suitable asset portfolios from Nexamp’s growing development and acquisition pipeline.
 










  
 Featured project 
 The largest privately owned solar project in Massachusetts when built in 2012, our 4.5-megawatt project in Westford represents the successful public-private partnerships that have made the Commonwealth a national leader in solar
 
