Nexamp, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 6:18 AM ET
Construction and Engineering

Company Overview of Nexamp, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Nexamp, Inc. operates as a solar contractor that designs, develops, builds, installs, owns, finances, and operates commercial-scale solar projects in the United States. The company offers asset management/operations and maintenance, power purchase agreements, and community solar solutions. It serves property owners and managers, energy users, solar facility owners, and investors. Nexamp, Inc. was founded in 2006 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts.


4 Liberty SquareBoston, MA 02109United StatesFounded in 2006



Phone: 617 431 1440

www.nexamp.com







