Why Work With Us




Why Work With Us

Nexamp is leading the way to the new energy economy with best-in-class solutions for commercial solar development, ownership, and operation. Our proven experience and comprehensive capabilities enable us to maximize the value of solar energy investments for all our partners. Nexamp’s expertise spans the entire solar project lifecycle, enabling us to deliver value at every step. Nexamp has a long list of commercial and utility-scale solar project successes and award-winning projects. The Nexamp team combines industry-leading solar expertise and experience with a passion for solutions that deliver breakthrough results. We are true believers in the power of solar to transform the energy mix.





More About Us




More About Us

As the leading solar energy solutions provider in the Northeast, Nexamp is making an impact every day. Our rapidly growing portfolio of solar assets and established partnerships with communities, commercial and non-profit organizations, property owners, and investors are laying the groundwork for a cleaner, more secure energy future. Solar Power World named Nexamp the Top Solar Contractor in Massachusetts and the #4 developer nationwide in 2014.






